5:
I can't believe our vacation comes
to an end today...
9:
What would you like to do? 
You don't have any jobs scheduled.
13:
Well, I was thinking we could ask
Gina for her recommendatio—
22:
Good morning, everyone! There's
something I wanted to ask—
30:
"Paradise Coliseum's Grand
Opening! The Dawn of a New
Fighting Craze Begins Today!"
33:
Th-that's right. It's an impromptu
event, so even the tourism
department just heard about it
today.
37:
Do you think they've got room 
for a last-minute entrant?
40:
Of course! They told us the more, 
the merrier!
44:
Then let's go! We'll make this
summer day shine brighter than
any other!
48:
What graceful swordsmanship! She
dances about the stage, yet she
doesn't leave a single opening!
50:
Moving on to the championship is
Shiiining Eclair!
53:
Thank you, one and all! 
Don't worry, I will continue to shine 
forth—all the way to the top!
58:
Wow... She's even more beautiful
here than at her poolside
performance!
65: You were great out there, Eclair.
69:
Thanks, but there's more where that
came from. Hope you're ready for
the next match.
72:
Why did you tell me about this
tournament?
75:
Well... Given your line of work, 
I figured it might pique your interest!
77:
And... What better way to promote
the coliseum than with Shining Eclair!
80:
Gina, I think I finally have an answer
for you.
83:
Ah, are you referring to my question
about what you'd do if you hadn't
joined the coliseum?
86:
Yes... I thought long and hard about
that question.
90:
But ultimately, I decided that I don't
care about what-if scenarios.
93:
The championship is about to
begin! Fighters, report to the stage!
99:
And that's what keeps me going. 
I want to set your heart ablaze, so
that it too can shine...
103:
So watch me, Gina. Watch me shine
even brighter than yesterday!
108:
That's it, folks! Introducing our new
champion... Shiiining Eclair!
110:
And so, our tournament comes to a
close... Or so you may think!
113:
You see, we've got a surprise in store
for our new champ!
116:
How thoughtful. I was just thinking
that last battle wasn’t enough to
quench my thirst.
119:
Come at me! Together, we'll give
these folks a brilliant finale!
123:
I must be faster and even more
graceful! I'll show you just how
strong and beautiful my sword is!
134:
And I hope my name burns bright
within your hearts till the end of time.
141:
All right, one final question: how was
your vacation?
146:
The word "fun" doesn't do it justice. 
It hurts my heart to have to say
goodbye to this lovely scenery.
149:
And... I get the feeling I learned more
about myself here.
152: Thank you for all you've done. Um...
155:
It sounds like you've got something
you want to say to me privately. Go
ahead.
158:
I... I want even more people to enjoy
this island!
160:
And I'll do whatever it takes as a
member of the tourism department
to make that happen!
163:
Well... As long as you keep at it, I'm
sure your path will open up.
166:
We're both walking down paths we
believe in, after all. We don't have
time to think about what-ifs.
176:
Back to the ol' coliseum. Are you
nervous?
181:
Hehe, still in interview mode, I see.
You'll have to watch my match for
your answer.
184:
By the way, I had a look at
"Passionate Platinum." I'm surprised
you cut our conversation on the
beach.
187:
I would've thought showing a more
vulnerable side was exactly what we
were looking for.
191:
Come on, you know us. We wouldn't
cut anything out.
196:
But we would keep a secret between
friends.
200:
I'm so glad you two and Gina were
the ones interviewing me... Now then!
204:
And now, the moment you've all
been waiting for—the return of our
undefeated arena beauty... Shiiining
Eclair!
207:
It's good to be back, everyone! 
And don't worry! I've brought enough
heat to make the summer sun
jealous!
211:
Watch as I burn brighter than the
sun!
